            <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/sports/basketball/mens">MEN&#039;S BASKETBALL</a></span></div>

                <h1>LeBron James gets first in-person look at Duke men&#039;s basketball in Charlottesville</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/85f7132d-19bb-4a6d-81ab-1b6b5643a4e7.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;LeBron&#x20;James&#x20;sat&#x20;courtside&#x20;at&#x20;John&#x20;Paul&#x20;Jones&#x20;Arena&#x20;Saturday&#x20;night&#x20;along&#x20;with&#x20;Lakers&#x20;teammate&#x20;Rajon&#x20;Rondo.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>LeBron James sat courtside at John Paul Jones Arena Saturday night along with Lakers teammate Rajon Rondo.</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/ian-jaffe">Ian Jaffe</a> |
